38859>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38859>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38859>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
38859>>>>>        Handle hoDD
38859>>>>>
38859>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
38860>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
38861>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
